{"tid":301320,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"嗰啲用 \"連登仔乜乜乜...\" 嚟抽水嘅人到底係諗緊啲咩 ?","createTime":"2017-06-28T14:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T14:33:16.000Z","uid":37125,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b336a29c8d476e7710d7e4398516ce1ada61e5","tid":301320,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"成日都見到啲人話 &quot;連登仔乜乜乜...&quot;. <br />\n例如: &quot;連登仔之前又話XXX, 而家一遇到YYY, 咪又係ZZZ.&quot;<br />\n咁請問你哋口中嘅 &quot;連登仔&quot; 係代表啲咩? 應該係指啲用緊 LIHKG 嘅人, 冇錯吧?  咁你係 LIHKG 講緊嘢, 咁即係你都係&quot;連登仔&quot;啦. 咁你係度講緊啲咩? 100步笑100步? 我唔明. <br />\n<br />\n就當講緊嘢嗰個人唔係 &quot;連登仔&quot;. 咁即係話A依個  &quot;連登仔&quot; 鍾意啜腳趾, 就代表全部&quot;連登仔&quot; 都鍾意啜腳趾? 快閃抽水法? 我更加唔明.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw, &quot;連登&quot; 依個名個人覺得好核突, 好大陸 feel."},{"pid":"35fa8b4d217081f38179c87661368ae0f13568f2","tid":301320,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:05:44.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"95f9abbcd45c1025e30c01160804508717470545","tid":301320,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1999</blockquote><br />\n有咩唔明?"},{"pid":"6dbaabddcca76ef606cd69fc7f8d2b3e86872ae3","tid":301320,"uid":57643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"新會然？"},{"pid":"a3e921bb7a599d703d83f5c9f8ef30719bf396a7","tid":301320,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新會然？</blockquote><br />\n我知由高登到依度都一直有依個問題, 但係都咁耐啦, 點解仲會講得出啲咁嘅嘢."}]}